title: New San Jose communications chief has on-the-job experience
text: San Jose Mayor Sam Liccardo has found a new chief spokesman, this time one with some experience in the job. Liccardo has tapped David Low -- the deputy communications director and longtime policy analyst for former Mayor Chuck Reed -- to be his new communications director. ...
